17
00:02:31,630 --> 00:02:33,000
Wait here. I'll go buy some for you.

18
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:33,610
Love you.

19
00:02:46,630 --> 00:02:47,470
Zishan.

20
00:02:49,190 --> 00:02:49,750
Zishan.

21
00:03:00,330 --> 00:03:01,150
Zishan.

22
00:03:03,150 --> 00:03:03,960
Doctor...

23
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:06,960
Dr. Luo.

24
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:10,440
You remember who I am.

25
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:14,020
Have you recalled something?

26
00:03:28,750 --> 00:03:30,190
Predestination

27
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:35,400
