29
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:42,820
Our meeting is predestined.

30
00:03:44,470 --> 00:03:45,440
The two of us

31
00:03:47,310 --> 00:03:49,870
are the best gifts
from Heaven to each other.

32
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:04,190
Liang.

33
00:04:18,310 --> 00:04:18,829
It's me.

34
00:04:21,430 --> 00:04:21,959
I'm here.

35
00:04:23,950 --> 00:04:25,210
I've always been here.

36
00:04:26,900 --> 00:04:28,370
I've never left you.

37
00:04:35,030 --> 00:04:37,650
[Qingzhu Hotel]

38
