48
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:15,930
Everything's here.

49
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:19,630
Luo and I...

50
00:05:22,830 --> 00:05:25,290
Xiao Su and I have just got married.

51
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:27,560
He probably hasn't had time to tell you.

52
00:05:27,830 --> 00:05:29,160
He has told me about it,

53
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:30,660
saying that you are

54
00:05:30,750 --> 00:05:32,040
a university teacher

55
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:34,100
and are well-educated and sensible.

56
00:05:36,750 --> 00:05:37,720
Where is Su?

57
00:05:38,270 --> 00:05:39,350
Is he also here?

58
00:05:40,659 --> 00:05:41,450
Yes.

59
00:05:42,159 --> 00:05:43,310
He knew that you

60
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:45,620
had taken Qiao Zishan from the hospital.

61
00:05:45,950 --> 00:05:47,080
He was very anxious,

62
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:49,430
so he rushed over here immediately.

63
00:05:49,430 --> 00:05:49,920
Then...

64
00:05:50,190 --> 00:05:50,990
Has he

65
00:05:51,070 --> 00:05:52,390
