66
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:54,490
Yes, he has.

67
00:05:55,830 --> 00:05:57,040
Where are they now?

68
00:05:57,270 --> 00:05:59,000
Are they alone together?

69
00:05:59,330 --> 00:06:00,700
Take me to see him now.

70
00:06:02,750 --> 00:06:04,280
What are you worried about?

71
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:11,360
Why did you take Qiao Zishan away

72
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:13,560
