75
00:06:26,190 --> 00:06:27,000
Liang.

76
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:30,430
Mom.

77
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:37,050
I'm looking for Mom.

78
00:06:38,270 --> 00:06:39,070
Where is Mom?

79
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:44,360
Your mom is dead.

80
00:06:46,430 --> 00:06:47,560
Don't you remember?

81
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:55,750
You killed your mom.

82
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:57,960
Have you forgotten that?

83
00:06:58,270 --> 00:06:59,430
I'm looking for Mom.

84
00:07:00,830 --> 00:07:02,360
Your mom was burnt to death.

85
00:07:06,830 --> 00:07:08,230
Your mom died miserably.

86
00:07:09,510 --> 00:07:10,910
And it was all your fault.

87
00:07:14,510 --> 00:07:15,560
It was a big fire.

88
00:07:17,870 --> 00:07:19,470
It was really such a big fire.

89
00:07:21,050 --> 00:07:21,790
Why?

90
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:24,570
Why didn't you save her?

91
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:27,440
It was such a big fire.

92
00:07:31,490 --> 00:07:33,110
Why did you kill your mom?

93
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:35,950
Zishan.

94
00:07:37,409 --> 00:07:38,610
Have you recalled it?

95
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:41,690
You took such good care of Qiao Zishan.

96
00:07:42,159 --> 00:07:44,560
How would you misremember her drug dosage?

97
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:46,750
I was muddle-headed.

98
00:07:46,750 --> 00:07:48,190
It was all my fault. I...

99
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:50,360
But your plan was very thorough.

100
00:07:50,870 --> 00:07:53,330
You brought Qiao Zishan
all the way out here,

101
00:07:53,390 --> 00:07:56,450
and neither the hospital
nor Xiao Su found out about it.

102
00:08:00,100 --> 00:08:01,930
Take me to see Zishan.

103
00:08:03,190 --> 00:08:06,510
You're very worried about
the two of them being together, right?

104
00:08:06,510 --> 00:08:08,480
No, no.

105
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:10,610
You were the one who burnt her to death.

106
00:08:13,870 --> 00:08:15,450
You just watched her burnt to death

107
00:08:15,450 --> 00:08:16,250
by the fire

108
00:08:17,450 --> 00:08:18,760
and did nothing.

109
00:08:19,440 --> 00:08:20,970
Your mom was in so much pain.

110
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:22,160
No.

111
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:25,290
She couldn't escape from there

112
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:26,950
and was just burnt to death like that.

113
00:08:26,950 --> 00:08:27,510
No.

114
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:28,790
Mom!

115
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:29,950
Mom!

116
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:33,039
Xiao Su is her psychiatrist.

117
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:35,240
He was the one who told you what medicine

118
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:36,120
and what dosage

119
00:08:36,630 --> 00:08:38,789
should be taken every day, right?

120
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:42,870
You noticed that Qiao Zishan still

121
00:08:42,870 --> 00:08:45,800
didn't get any better
after taking so much medicine,

122
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:48,570
so you took her to the hospital.

123
00:08:49,860 --> 00:08:51,920
But the police discovered a problem.

124
00:08:52,330 --> 00:08:54,260
Do you know how much pain she was in?

125
00:08:55,670 --> 00:08:57,270
You would be in pain too, huh?

126
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:59,590
But your mother's pain was 10 times
or even 100 times stronger than yours.

127
00:08:59,590 --> 00:09:00,750
When she was found,

128
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:02,620
she didn't have any skin left.

129
00:09:03,030 --> 00:09:04,720
But Xiao Su is your son.

130
00:09:06,340 --> 00:09:09,200
And you couldn't tell the police
these suspicions.

131
00:09:09,550 --> 00:09:12,410
-Zishan.
-But you also want to protect Qiao Zishan.

132
00:09:12,510 --> 00:09:14,770
So you could only take her away secretly.

133
00:09:15,510 --> 00:09:16,320
Is that right?

134
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:17,840
How could you kill your mom?

135
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:19,430
-I didn't!
-Why did you kill your mom?

136
00:09:19,430 --> 00:09:20,980
Why did you kill her?

137
00:09:21,270 --> 00:09:23,320
It would be great if Mom has disappeared.

138
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:25,320
No! No!

139
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:27,840
Mom!

140
00:09:27,880 --> 00:09:29,910
Mom, I'm sorry!

141
00:09:30,670 --> 00:09:32,600
Xiao Su isn't like this.

142
00:09:32,670 --> 00:09:34,040
No!

143
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:37,200
Mom!

144
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:40,440
Mom!

145
00:09:42,030 --> 00:09:42,870
Xiao Su

146
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:45,980
