154
00:10:18,270 --> 00:10:18,840
Su.

155
00:10:25,670 --> 00:10:26,890
-Sister?
-Yuan?

156
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:28,840
Mom.

157
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:35,750
