168
00:11:06,810 --> 00:11:09,610
[Xinhua Dictionary]

169
00:11:07,860 --> 00:11:10,060
Who did you sleep with to get this money?

170
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:15,840
You little scoundrel!

171
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:16,840
What are you doing?

172
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:17,320
What happened?

173
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:17,960
What happened?

174
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:19,200
What's on your underpants?

175
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:20,240
I'll beat you to death!

176
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:21,200
Don't hit him.

177
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:22,870
I didn't do anything. I just had a dream.

178
00:11:22,870 --> 00:11:25,000
If you keep hitting him like this,
I'll take him away!

179
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:26,960
