185
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:36,530
Get lost! Get lost, all of you!

186
00:11:36,630 --> 00:11:37,320
Look at you.

187
00:11:37,550 --> 00:11:38,360
As soon as you came back,

188
00:11:38,360 --> 00:11:40,090
