189
00:11:40,390 --> 00:11:41,720
How shameless!

190
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:42,890
No.

191
00:11:43,750 --> 00:11:45,220
I just had a dream.

192
00:11:46,040 --> 00:11:47,970
I really don't know what happened.

193
00:11:53,030 --> 00:11:53,870
Yuan!

194
00:11:54,510 --> 00:11:55,050
Sister!

195
00:11:55,270 --> 00:11:55,990
Sister!

196
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:57,080
Sister!

197
00:11:57,510 --> 00:11:58,870
Su! Su!

198
00:11:59,870 --> 00:12:00,650
I'll never

199
00:12:00,870 --> 00:12:02,390
come back to this home again!

200
00:12:02,390 --> 00:12:03,030
Sister!

201
00:12:03,510 --> 00:12:04,510
Wait for me!

202
00:12:05,670 --> 00:12:06,270
Sister!

203
00:12:07,150 --> 00:12:08,810
Take me with you to leave here!

204
00:12:08,840 --> 00:12:09,720
His father...

205
00:12:11,270 --> 00:12:14,080
was a dirty-minded beast himself.

206
00:12:16,030 --> 00:12:16,670
So,

207
00:12:18,130 --> 00:12:20,390
