208
00:12:22,140 --> 00:12:23,140
Xiao Su

209
00:12:25,210 --> 00:12:26,260
and his sister

210
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:32,080
were both ruined by him.

211
00:12:43,130 --> 00:12:44,480
Step back, everyone!

212
00:12:44,480 --> 00:12:46,240
Guys, please cooperate!

213
00:12:50,120 --> 00:12:51,520
Guys, please cooperate!

214
00:12:51,960 --> 00:12:53,030
Don't block the way, you all.

215
00:12:53,030 --> 00:12:55,230
Step aside! Let me through! Step aside!

216
00:13:05,270 --> 00:13:06,430
We found Qiao Zishan.

217
00:13:06,430 --> 00:13:08,030
She's at the police station.

218
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:09,530
Let's go.

219
00:13:10,630 --> 00:13:11,300
Hurry up!

220
00:13:11,630 --> 00:13:12,440
Be careful!

221
00:13:15,880 --> 00:13:18,030
[Xincheng Police Station, Kangjia Road Branch,
Tanhua Public Security Bureau]

222
00:13:28,330 --> 00:13:30,600
[Case Filing Chamber,
Sunday, July 21, 2019]

223
00:13:30,650 --> 00:13:33,670
[Police]

224
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:35,190
Let go of her! Let go!

225
00:13:35,480 --> 00:13:36,880
Zishan! Zishan! Come on!

226
00:13:38,910 --> 00:13:39,550
No!

227
00:13:40,120 --> 00:13:42,290
It's okay. I'm here.

228
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:43,080
Zishan.

229
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:45,080
We are the police.

230
00:13:46,270 --> 00:13:47,000
Come with us.

231
00:13:47,840 --> 00:13:49,790
The police will protect you
and keep you safe.

232
00:13:49,790 --> 00:13:50,410
Okay?

233
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:52,340
Don't get close to her.

234
00:13:52,510 --> 00:13:54,200
She's emotionally unstable now.

235
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:55,720
If I was one minute late at that time,

236
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:58,250
she would've jumped down
from that buidling.

237
00:14:00,120 --> 00:14:00,670
Zishan.

238
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:02,840
Zishan.

239
00:14:03,790 --> 00:14:05,390
We've met before. Remember?

240
00:14:06,840 --> 00:14:07,600
Don't worry.

241
00:14:08,480 --> 00:14:09,270
If someone tries to hurt you,

242
00:14:09,270 --> 00:14:10,130
you can tell me,

243
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:12,280
and I'll definitely arrest him.

244
00:14:13,150 --> 00:14:14,350
Come with the police.

245
00:14:17,790 --> 00:14:19,440
The police will protect you
and keep you safe.

246
00:14:19,440 --> 00:14:19,870
Okay?

247
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:28,360
I killed my mom!

248
00:14:30,510 --> 00:14:32,240
Mom... I killed

249
00:14:32,240 --> 00:14:32,860
my mom!

250
00:14:33,670 --> 00:14:35,400
Now that she has become like this,

251
00:14:35,400 --> 00:14:37,660
you guys are largely responsible for it.

252
00:14:37,920 --> 00:14:39,550
My mom said she was fine at first.

253
00:14:39,550 --> 00:14:40,630
Without considering

254
00:14:40,630 --> 00:14:41,670
her condition,

255
00:14:41,670 --> 00:14:43,150
you guys forcibly hypnotized her.

256
00:14:43,150 --> 00:14:45,550
We've evaluated the risks
of hypnotizing her.

257
00:14:45,550 --> 00:14:47,600
The police's case-handling procedures
are reasonable and lawful.

258
00:14:47,600 --> 00:14:49,260
We don't need to report to you.

259
00:14:50,390 --> 00:14:51,190
Let me ask you.

260
00:14:51,670 --> 00:14:53,870
Why did your mom take her away secretly?

261
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:57,290
Because my mom knew that

262
00:14:57,910 --> 00:14:59,970
if you found out she was not my sister,

263
00:15:00,210 --> 00:15:01,320
you would take away

264
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:03,120
her only spiritual sustenance.

265
00:15:06,120 --> 00:15:07,780
If you cared about her so much,

266
00:15:08,110 --> 00:15:10,910
why did your mom take her away
without telling you?

267
00:15:11,240 --> 00:15:11,940
Mom.

268
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:13,600
Because my mom knew very well

269
00:15:13,910 --> 00:15:15,910
I wouldn't let her take Zishan away.

270
00:15:16,960 --> 00:15:17,600
When she disappeared,

271
00:15:17,600 --> 00:15:19,530
