272
00:15:19,870 --> 00:15:21,330
If I had called the police,

273
00:15:21,360 --> 00:15:23,360
wouldn't my mom become an abductor?

274
00:15:23,960 --> 00:15:25,750
But now that I've found Zishan,

275
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:28,000
my mom's problem is not that serious.

276
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:29,420
Right, Officer Li?

277
00:15:32,960 --> 00:15:34,870
I don't believe in a single word you say,

278
00:15:34,870 --> 00:15:35,670
Dr. Luo.

279
00:15:38,350 --> 00:15:40,080
-Don't worry. I'm here.
-Mom.

280
00:15:40,080 --> 00:15:40,810
Where's Mom?

281
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:43,600
Mom.

282
00:15:47,790 --> 00:15:48,390
Mom.

283
00:15:48,790 --> 00:15:50,550
No!

284
00:15:51,910 --> 00:15:53,030
Mom!

285
00:15:53,510 --> 00:15:55,540
Mom!

286
00:15:55,630 --> 00:15:57,480
Mom!

287
00:15:58,550 --> 00:15:59,870
Mom!

288
00:16:01,790 --> 00:16:02,440
Hello?

289
00:16:03,120 --> 00:16:04,450
The police has found me.

290
00:16:04,480 --> 00:16:06,070
I think they've tracked down your car.

291
00:16:06,070 --> 00:16:07,330
They'll find you soon.

292
00:16:08,150 --> 00:16:08,720
Mom!

293
00:16:09,440 --> 00:16:10,150
Mom!

294
00:16:11,030 --> 00:16:12,000
Mom!

295
00:16:13,120 --> 00:16:13,680
Mom!

296
00:16:13,910 --> 00:16:15,570
Mom!

297
00:16:16,600 --> 00:16:17,390
Mom!

298
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:19,030
Mom!

299
00:16:19,790 --> 00:16:21,320
Mom!

300
00:16:22,720 --> 00:16:24,380
No one will forgive you,

301
00:16:24,400 --> 00:16:25,320
except me.

302
00:16:27,510 --> 00:16:30,770
I'm the one who understands you the best
in the whole world.

303
00:16:31,360 --> 00:16:32,280
I know you well.

304
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:33,960
I'll forgive you.

305
00:16:36,720 --> 00:16:38,120
I won't let anyone know

306
00:16:38,470 --> 00:16:40,470
that you've killed someone before.

307
00:16:41,560 --> 00:16:42,960
For the rest of your life,

308
00:16:43,420 --> 00:16:44,820
you must always remember

309
00:16:45,870 --> 00:16:47,870
you were the one who killed your mom.

310
00:16:48,910 --> 00:16:50,940
You were the one who killed your mom.

311
00:16:57,020 --> 00:16:59,320
I was the one who killed my mom.

312
00:17:05,030 --> 00:17:05,920
I'm sorry.

313
00:17:07,690 --> 00:17:08,440
I'm sorry.

314
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:10,160
I'm sorry.

315
00:17:10,640 --> 00:17:11,310
I'm sorry.

316
00:17:13,349 --> 00:17:15,170
Mom! Mom!

317
00:17:17,480 --> 00:17:18,240
Mom!

318
00:17:19,589 --> 00:17:20,640
I killed her.

319
00:17:21,200 --> 00:17:22,810
I killed her!

320
00:17:23,109 --> 00:17:24,109
Mom!

321
00:17:24,050 --> 00:17:26,200
[Xincheng Police Station, Kangjia Road Branch,
Tanhua Public Security Bureau]

322
00:17:41,570 --> 00:17:43,080
[Please go upstairs from this way]

323
00:17:43,080 --> 00:17:44,530
[No smoking]

324
00:17:45,880 --> 00:17:47,690
Officers,
there's no need to trouble you two.

325
00:17:47,690 --> 00:17:49,690
I can explain it to my mother myself.

326
00:17:50,350 --> 00:17:51,510
This is no trouble at all.

327
00:17:51,510 --> 00:17:53,170
We need to handle it to the end.

328
00:18:10,310 --> 00:18:11,110
Honey.

329
00:18:15,830 --> 00:18:17,270
Why are you two together?

330
00:18:19,440 --> 00:18:20,500
As soon as you left,

331
00:18:20,680 --> 00:18:23,310
I got a call from Officer Li,
and he was looking for you.

332
00:18:23,310 --> 00:18:25,970
He said they got a notice
from the Wuzhou police.

333
00:18:26,350 --> 00:18:28,520
Mom took Qiao Zishan away.

334
00:18:28,680 --> 00:18:31,720
They both went to Tanhua,
and he asked whether you knew it.

335
00:18:31,720 --> 00:18:32,960
I couldn't find you.

336
00:18:33,350 --> 00:18:35,950
I got so worried
that I just came here directly.

337
00:18:38,510 --> 00:18:40,170
I'm sorry to have worried you.

338
00:18:41,440 --> 00:18:43,000
Mom, are you okay?

339
00:18:47,830 --> 00:18:49,480
Everything's been clearly explained now,

340
00:18:49,480 --> 00:18:50,270
officers.

341
00:18:52,640 --> 00:18:54,510
Ma'am, why did you take Qiao Zishan away?

342
00:18:54,510 --> 00:18:55,310
Officer Li,

343
00:18:55,720 --> 00:18:57,380
whatever misunderstandings

344
00:18:57,510 --> 00:18:59,240
you might have about us before,

345
00:18:59,720 --> 00:19:02,050
we have cooperated in every way we should.

346
00:19:02,240 --> 00:19:03,440
If you have any proof,

347
00:19:03,590 --> 00:19:05,000
just arrest him.

348
00:19:05,270 --> 00:19:06,240
If you don't,

349
00:19:06,750 --> 00:19:08,010
please leave us alone.

350
00:19:08,550 --> 00:19:09,770
Luo Liang rushed over

351
00:19:10,070 --> 00:19:11,350
and found Qiao Zishan.

352
00:19:11,680 --> 00:19:14,090
My mother-in-law made a foolish mistake
by taking her away,

353
00:19:14,090 --> 00:19:15,920
but nothing serious happened in the end.

354
00:19:15,920 --> 00:19:16,640
Right?

355
00:19:18,160 --> 00:19:19,090
I implore you

356
00:19:19,960 --> 00:19:21,420
to end the whole thing now.

357
00:19:22,270 --> 00:19:23,030
Ms. Yan...

358
00:19:23,440 --> 00:19:25,170
If you do think of me as a friend,

359
00:19:26,270 --> 00:19:27,800
then don't hurt us anymore.

360
00:19:29,000 --> 00:19:31,260
Stop hurting my husband, in particular.

361
00:19:35,830 --> 00:19:37,360
Just like me, it was not easy

362
00:19:38,200 --> 00:19:40,260
for Luo Liang to get where he is today.

363
00:19:41,070 --> 00:19:42,530
Put an end to this fuss now,

364
00:19:42,680 --> 00:19:43,210
will you?

365
00:19:49,070 --> 00:19:49,440
Mom.

366
00:19:49,590 --> 00:19:50,190
Ms. Yan...

367
00:19:50,310 --> 00:19:52,160
My wife has made it very clear.

368
00:19:52,750 --> 00:19:54,480
Target me if anything comes up.

369
00:19:55,160 --> 00:19:56,690
Just leave my family alone.

370
00:20:01,070 --> 00:20:02,410
My number is on this card.

371
00:20:02,410 --> 00:20:03,140
[Name: Li Zhiheng]

372
00:20:03,550 --> 00:20:05,160
I'll contact you anytime

373
00:20:05,160 --> 00:20:06,890
if your cooperation is needed.

374
00:20:09,070 --> 00:20:10,350
Mom, let's go.

375
00:20:11,110 --> 00:20:11,720
Let me carry it.

376
00:20:11,720 --> 00:20:13,110
Let's go, Mom.

377
00:20:26,550 --> 00:20:27,810
What is all this about?

378
00:20:31,310 --> 00:20:32,110
Has Ms. Yan...

379
00:20:33,440 --> 00:20:34,900
really been brainwashed?

380
00:20:36,160 --> 00:20:39,190
[Nanhuguan Long-distance
Passenger Transport Station]

381
00:20:38,960 --> 00:20:40,030
About Zishan...

382
00:20:42,240 --> 00:20:43,880
She has been taken away by the police.

383
00:20:43,880 --> 00:20:44,790
-Thank you.
-They'll take care of her.

384
00:20:44,790 --> 00:20:46,920
-Don't worry.
-That's the bus, right?

385
00:20:46,920 --> 00:20:49,650
You didn't let anything slip to Yan Ling,
did you?

386
00:20:50,920 --> 00:20:52,550
Mom, here's your ticket.

387
00:20:56,960 --> 00:20:59,330
Actually, Luo Liang and I
have talked about it.

388
00:20:59,330 --> 00:21:00,480
If you want to,

389
00:21:00,510 --> 00:21:02,140
just come home with us.

390
00:21:02,020 --> 00:21:04,690
[Jinhu Transport]

391
00:21:03,640 --> 00:21:04,440
Yes, Mom.

392
00:21:05,480 --> 00:21:07,740
Yan Ling and I will respect your opinion.

393
00:21:10,180 --> 00:21:11,790
I'd better go back.

394
00:21:12,920 --> 00:21:13,840
That will

395
00:21:14,430 --> 00:21:15,490
put my mind at ease.

396
00:21:16,350 --> 00:21:18,400
I agree. Let Mom go back.

397
00:21:19,070 --> 00:21:21,070
Only Diannan feels like home to her.

398
00:21:27,350 --> 00:21:29,070
Make sure you treat Ling well.

399
00:21:31,270 --> 00:21:31,970
Of course.

400
00:21:32,350 --> 00:21:33,680
She's my wife after all.

401
00:21:38,460 --> 00:21:40,090
Take care.

402
00:21:42,510 --> 00:21:44,110
Don't compromise yourself.

403
00:21:49,790 --> 00:21:51,090
Mom, get on the bus now.

404
00:21:51,510 --> 00:21:52,640
It's about to leave.

405
00:21:56,070 --> 00:21:57,800
I'll visit you when I have time.

406
00:22:51,510 --> 00:22:52,440
Su!

407
00:22:54,510 --> 00:22:55,350
Yuan!

408
00:23:02,580 --> 00:23:03,280
Su...

409
00:23:37,240 --> 00:23:38,170
Thank you so much

410
00:23:38,830 --> 00:23:41,490
for defending me
in front of the police just now.

411
00:23:41,510 --> 00:23:42,840
As you just said,

412
00:23:43,550 --> 00:23:44,880
I am your wife after all.

413
00:23:46,750 --> 00:23:48,210
Ever since my sister left,

414
00:23:48,790 --> 00:23:50,720
no one has protected me like you do.

415
00:23:53,110 --> 00:23:53,970
Let the bygones

416
00:23:54,880 --> 00:23:56,240
be bygones.

417
00:24:07,440 --> 00:24:08,240
Let's go home.

418
00:25:28,210 --> 00:25:32,030
[List of devices]

419
00:25:44,940 --> 00:25:49,800
