[July 21, 2019, Sunday]

441
00:27:25,880 --> 00:27:26,410
Hey,

442
00:27:26,440 --> 00:27:27,700
property management?

443
00:27:27,830 --> 00:27:28,420
Hello.

444
00:27:29,510 --> 00:27:31,570
I'm the owner of Unit 808, Building B.

445
00:27:31,750 --> 00:27:32,720
I'd like to ask

446
00:27:33,240 --> 00:27:35,570
why the power suddenly went out
at my place

447
00:27:35,750 --> 00:27:37,010
the night before last.

448
00:27:37,590 --> 00:27:39,450
Is there any maintenance record?

449
00:27:41,200 --> 00:27:42,310
The fuse was blown?

450
00:27:44,400 --> 00:27:46,460
A short circuit in the incoming wire?

451
00:27:49,830 --> 00:27:50,440
Got it.

452
00:27:51,680 --> 00:27:52,350
Thank you.

453
00:28:07,640 --> 00:28:08,640
Look at each other,

454
00:28:08,640 --> 00:28:10,070
with deep affection.

455
00:28:10,070 --> 00:28:12,240
One, two, three. Terrific!

456
00:28:12,310 --> 00:28:12,960
One more photo.

457
00:28:12,960 --> 00:28:14,750
One, two, three. Good!

458
00:28:14,750 --> 00:28:16,030
Puff out your chests a bit more. Yes.

459
00:28:16,030 --> 00:28:17,350
Puff out your chests, please.

460
00:28:17,350 --> 00:28:18,670
One, two, three.

461
00:28:18,790 --> 00:28:20,720
Okay. Look each other in the eye again.

462
00:28:20,720 --> 00:28:22,640
One, two, three. Here it goes!

463
00:28:22,720 --> 00:28:23,510
You're doing great.

464
00:28:23,510 --> 00:28:24,000
That's right.

465
00:28:24,000 --> 00:28:24,790
I like the vibes.

466
00:28:24,790 --> 00:28:25,510
Very good.

467
00:28:25,510 --> 00:28:27,210
This is so nice. Alright!

468
00:28:27,400 --> 00:28:28,640
Good. Look at me now.

469
00:28:28,920 --> 00:28:31,170
Okay. One, two, three.

470
00:28:45,720 --> 00:28:46,800
This way, please.

471
00:28:50,680 --> 00:28:51,830
The bride takes this room.

472
00:28:51,830 --> 00:28:52,160
Okay.

473
00:28:53,680 --> 00:28:55,000
And the groom takes this one.

474
00:28:55,000 --> 00:28:55,800
Okay, thanks.

475
00:28:57,590 --> 00:28:58,200
Honey.

476
00:29:05,480 --> 00:29:06,080
What's up?

477
00:29:09,720 --> 00:29:10,510
The last time

478
00:29:11,400 --> 00:29:13,660
we tried to get our wedding photos taken,

479
00:29:13,680 --> 00:29:15,280
your mother had an accident.

480
00:29:15,310 --> 00:29:17,710
I never brought up
the photo shooting again

481
00:29:18,160 --> 00:29:19,620
for fear of upsetting you.

482
00:29:21,920 --> 00:29:24,850
But this time,
you took the initiative to propose it.

483
00:29:25,440 --> 00:29:26,440
I'm very touched.

484
00:29:33,790 --> 00:29:36,650
We are going to spend
the rest of our lives together.

485
00:29:36,960 --> 00:29:38,960
Had better tie up all the loose ends.

486
00:29:48,790 --> 00:29:49,920
I'll go get changed.

487
00:29:49,960 --> 00:29:50,640
Okay.

488
00:29:55,640 --> 00:29:56,930
[Outpatient Clinic]

489
00:29:58,670 --> 00:30:00,780
[Outpatient Clinic]

