499
00:31:05,930 --> 00:31:06,590
Chen,

500
00:31:07,400 --> 00:31:09,310
get a glycerin enema to Bed 53.

501
00:31:09,360 --> 00:31:11,820
The patient said
he is a little constipated.

502
00:31:41,190 --> 00:31:43,160
[Smile Service, Warm as Always]

503
00:32:29,400 --> 00:32:30,410
If you miss Jiale,

504
00:32:30,960 --> 00:32:32,050
just call him.

505
00:32:32,880 --> 00:32:33,720
As his mother,

506
00:32:34,240 --> 00:32:36,040
you should take the initiative.

507
00:32:38,790 --> 00:32:39,810
I'd rather not.

508
00:32:41,160 --> 00:32:43,680
I'm afraid Jiale hasn't forgiven me yet.

509
00:32:48,510 --> 00:32:50,480
It's said that a mother and child
share a special bond.

510
00:32:50,480 --> 00:32:51,810
Jiale is a sensible kid.

511
00:32:52,400 --> 00:32:55,330
No matter how angry he was,
he should be over it by now.

512
00:33:01,240 --> 00:33:03,440
I'll make the call for you, if you don't.

513
00:33:05,200 --> 00:33:07,140
[Jiale]

514
00:33:18,270 --> 00:33:18,880
Hello?

515
00:33:21,270 --> 00:33:22,110
Jiale,

516
00:33:22,640 --> 00:33:23,550
this is Mom.

517
00:33:24,440 --> 00:33:25,510
I miss you.

518
00:33:33,310 --> 00:33:35,410
A day apart feels like three years.

519
00:33:36,550 --> 00:33:37,400
Jiale,

520
00:33:38,030 --> 00:33:39,310
your mom misses you so much

521
00:33:39,310 --> 00:33:41,170
that she's aging into an old lady.

522
00:33:45,110 --> 00:33:48,000
Jiale, I admit I was wrong.

523
00:33:48,440 --> 00:33:49,510
Can you forgive me?

524
00:33:55,590 --> 00:33:56,850
How about this, Jiale?

525
00:33:57,310 --> 00:33:59,320
We'll take you hiking in a few days.

526
00:33:59,510 --> 00:34:01,590
Your mom and I will pick you up, okay?

527
00:34:02,730 --> 00:34:04,040
The weather's too hot lately.

528
00:34:04,040 --> 00:34:05,090
I don't want to go.

529
00:34:05,830 --> 00:34:07,920
No problem. It's up to you.

530
00:34:16,389 --> 00:34:18,989
I'll call you again in a few days,
little buddy.

531
00:34:19,590 --> 00:34:20,190
Bye.

532
00:34:20,760 --> 00:34:21,550
Bye, big bro.

533
00:34:32,230 --> 00:34:34,000
He's still mad at me.

534
00:34:35,320 --> 00:34:36,110
It's okay.

535
00:34:37,440 --> 00:34:38,770
Give him some more time.

536
00:35:20,710 --> 00:35:21,910
What are you cooking?

537
00:35:22,510 --> 00:35:23,510
Small wontons.

538
00:35:24,710 --> 00:35:25,550
Try some.

539
00:35:26,230 --> 00:35:26,960
Sure.

540
00:35:26,960 --> 00:35:28,000
Careful, it's hot.

541
00:35:28,000 --> 00:35:28,800
Okay.

542
00:35:29,110 --> 00:35:30,110
Here's cilantro.

543
00:35:42,280 --> 00:35:42,920
So tasty.

544
00:35:56,230 --> 00:35:57,030
Are you happy?

545
00:35:58,800 --> 00:35:59,480
What?

546
00:36:01,670 --> 00:36:02,600
That pen holder.

547
00:36:03,320 --> 00:36:05,440
I found it in Mom's bag that day.

548
00:36:06,590 --> 00:36:08,550
She said you got it from your sister
as a gift,

549
00:36:08,550 --> 00:36:10,030
and that you liked it so much

550
00:36:10,030 --> 00:36:11,440
that you'd take it everywhere with you.

551
00:36:11,440 --> 00:36:13,710
It was not until you started working
that you sent it back home.

552
00:36:13,710 --> 00:36:16,110
I know you were very close
with your sister,

553
00:36:16,850 --> 00:36:18,710
so I asked Mom for this pen holder.

554
00:36:21,630 --> 00:36:23,560
Why didn't you tell me beforehand?

555
00:36:25,030 --> 00:36:26,890
Because I wanted to surprise you.

556
00:36:34,110 --> 00:36:35,440
I noticed

557
00:36:35,710 --> 00:36:36,640
the broken parts

558
00:36:37,150 --> 00:36:38,010
here and there.

559
00:36:38,230 --> 00:36:40,550
I meant to have the item fixed
before bringing it back to you.

560
00:36:40,550 --> 00:36:41,950
However, I asked around—

561
00:36:42,230 --> 00:36:45,150
watch repairers, appliance repairers,
car mechanics—

562
00:36:45,150 --> 00:36:46,460
but no one could fix it.

563
00:36:46,840 --> 00:36:48,640
So I had to bring it back as it was.

564
00:36:51,480 --> 00:36:52,280
Thank you.

565
00:37:02,840 --> 00:37:04,030
Are you not happy?

566
00:37:07,280 --> 00:37:08,280
Why would I not be?

567
00:37:44,490 --> 00:37:50,190
[July 26, 2019 Friday]

568
00:37:52,680 --> 00:37:55,530
[July 26, 2019 Friday]

