00:38:21,440 --> 00:38:21,960
Yes.

575
00:38:31,960 --> 00:38:32,360
Hello?

576
00:38:32,720 --> 00:38:33,320
Dr. Luo,

577
00:38:33,920 --> 00:38:34,980
this is Officer Li.

578
00:38:36,190 --> 00:38:36,920
Officer Li,

579
00:38:37,480 --> 00:38:38,280
what is it now?

580
00:38:39,480 --> 00:38:41,800
Could you come to the police station now?

581
00:38:43,880 --> 00:38:44,480
Right now?

582
00:38:45,710 --> 00:38:46,360
Sorry.

583
00:38:46,800 --> 00:38:48,030
This is not a proper time.

584
00:38:48,030 --> 00:38:48,890
I'm on duty now.

585
00:38:50,070 --> 00:38:51,930
Didn't Yan Ling already tell you?

586
00:38:52,280 --> 00:38:54,540
We've cooperated in every way we should.

587
00:38:55,150 --> 00:38:57,080
Please stop disturbing our lives.

588
00:38:57,480 --> 00:38:58,150
Here's the thing.

589
00:38:58,150 --> 00:38:59,400
Regarding Qiao Zishan's case,

590
00:38:59,400 --> 00:39:01,200
we need to take some statements.

591
00:39:01,480 --> 00:39:02,960
Every citizen is obligated to cooperate

592
00:39:02,960 --> 00:39:04,620
with police investigations.

593
00:39:05,360 --> 00:39:06,690
Please be cooperative,

594
00:39:06,760 --> 00:39:07,440
will you?

595
00:39:12,030 --> 00:39:12,550
Fine.

596
00:39:17,250 --> 00:39:19,180
[Loyal to the Party, Serve the People]

597
00:39:18,000 --> 00:39:18,400
Sit.

598
00:39:26,400 --> 00:39:27,310
Relax.

599
00:39:27,440 --> 00:39:28,440
We just need a statement from you.

600
00:39:28,440 --> 00:39:29,840
It's routine procedure.

601
00:39:36,760 --> 00:39:38,960
Qiao Zishan's condition has improved.

602
00:39:40,550 --> 00:39:41,110
Really?

603
00:39:42,000 --> 00:39:43,060
That's great news.

604
00:39:44,670 --> 00:39:47,110
But she insists
that she knocked down her mother

605
00:39:47,110 --> 00:39:48,890
by accident during the fire.

606
00:39:49,000 --> 00:39:50,230
So, over all these years,

607
00:39:50,230 --> 00:39:51,190
she's been beating herself up,

608
00:39:51,190 --> 00:39:53,450
thinking that she killed her own mother.

609
00:39:56,360 --> 00:39:58,020
Her life is miserable enough.

610
00:39:58,800 --> 00:40:00,590
Frankly speaking, I really don't know

611
00:40:00,590 --> 00:40:02,320
why you have to add to her pain.

612
00:40:03,230 --> 00:40:05,360
The guilt and self-blame
weighing on her heart

613
00:40:05,360 --> 00:40:07,190
have exceeded what she can take.

614
00:40:08,000 --> 00:40:09,460
This is why she broke down,

615
00:40:10,030 --> 00:40:12,560
and her mental state didn't improve
in years.

616
00:40:15,800 --> 00:40:16,760
We retrieved the forensic report

617
00:40:16,760 --> 00:40:19,360
written by the Harbor Island police
back then.

618
00:40:19,590 --> 00:40:20,480
This report shows

619
00:40:20,480 --> 00:40:22,670
that Qiao Zishan's mother, Qiao Lihua,

620
00:40:22,670 --> 00:40:25,270
did have multiple injuries
caused by tumbles.

621
00:40:25,880 --> 00:40:27,280
But recently, we sent the report

622
00:40:27,280 --> 00:40:28,920
to a rather experienced forensic expert

623
00:40:28,920 --> 00:40:29,840
in the mainland.

624
00:40:29,840 --> 00:40:30,840
He pointed out...

625
00:40:33,280 --> 00:40:35,530
that there was a radiating fracture

626
00:40:36,000 --> 00:40:38,030
on the left temporal side
of the deceased's skull,

627
00:40:38,030 --> 00:40:40,430
likely resulting from blunt force trauma.

628
00:40:49,190 --> 00:40:49,880
Sorry,

629
00:40:49,880 --> 00:40:50,540
Officer Li.

630
00:40:51,590 --> 00:40:52,920
I am a psychiatrist

631
00:40:53,840 --> 00:40:56,190
who has no expertise in forensic science.

632
00:40:58,630 --> 00:40:59,430
I understand.

633
00:41:00,880 --> 00:41:02,540
Today, I asked you to come over

634
00:41:02,630 --> 00:41:04,440
because I'd like you to tell me

635
00:41:05,000 --> 00:41:06,440
if there was anyone else

636
00:41:06,880 --> 00:41:08,440
than you, Qiao Zishan, and her mother

637
00:41:07,020 --> 00:41:10,960
[Suspected to be caused by a blunt object
with a curved impact face]

638
00:41:09,230 --> 00:41:10,760
at the fire scene years ago.

639
00:41:11,200 --> 00:41:12,840
Could someone have caused this injury

640
00:41:12,840 --> 00:41:14,460
by hitting Qiao Lihua in the head

641
00:41:14,460 --> 00:41:15,840
with a heavy object?

642
00:41:24,070 --> 00:41:25,470
I can't recall anything.

643
00:41:26,030 --> 00:41:28,530
All I can remember
is that the whole place was a total mess

644
00:41:28,530 --> 00:41:30,330
when the fire fighters arrived.

645
00:41:35,640 --> 00:41:40,010
[Suspected to be caused by a blunt object
with a curved impact face]

646
00:41:38,800 --> 00:41:40,410
It says "suspected."

647
00:41:40,550 --> 00:41:42,670
Could it have been caused

648
00:41:42,670 --> 00:41:43,840
by the burned furniture

649
00:41:43,840 --> 00:41:45,440
or some sort of heavy object?

650
00:41:46,230 --> 00:41:48,430
That could be a possibility, of course.

651
00:41:48,880 --> 00:41:50,630
But according to the forensic expert,

652
00:41:50,630 --> 00:41:53,590
the contact surface of the wound
suggests the assault weapon

653
00:41:53,590 --> 00:41:55,650
should be a sphere-shaped object.

654
00:41:56,590 --> 00:41:58,920
Furniture doesn't fit that description.

655
00:42:00,850 --> 00:42:03,180
Back then, in Dr. Tao's office,

656
00:42:04,070 --> 00:42:04,760
was there

657
00:42:05,590 --> 00:42:07,720
any heavy object resembling a sphere?

658
00:42:10,960 --> 00:42:11,960
I don't remember.

659
00:42:16,480 --> 00:42:17,680
Well, that's a shame.

660
00:42:19,190 --> 00:42:21,120
See, if we really find this object,

661
00:42:21,800 --> 00:42:23,280
with current technology,

662
00:42:23,300 --> 00:42:26,050
as long as there is a tiny bit
of biological residue on it,

663
00:42:26,050 --> 00:42:27,850
we'll be able to find DNA traces.

664
00:42:28,480 --> 00:42:30,810
Then the truth will be revealed, won't it?

665
00:42:31,070 --> 00:42:31,880
It can also save you

666
00:42:31,880 --> 00:42:33,280
the trouble of coming over
every now and then

667
00:42:33,280 --> 00:42:34,960
to assist us with the investigation.

668
00:42:34,960 --> 00:42:35,360
Right?

669
00:42:38,880 --> 00:42:40,680
I'm terribly sorry, Officer Li,

670
00:42:41,670 --> 00:42:43,270
for not being helpful at all.

671
00:42:44,260 --> 00:42:48,790
[The Dark Romance]
